captions.text: First time i met them was 4 years ago. I can see their skills have greatly progressed, so its difficult to judge.
Overall, various technical skills, speedy movements, and accuracy have improved in the scene
It was definitely a tough battle.
Nao showed aggressive attitude with great skills, which gave him high marks.
I could see Tokura was trying to do the best he could and in the end he did it!
My strategy until the semi-final was to keep big tricks until the final and perform well with other tricks. I guess it worked.
That way I could concentrate on improving skills and accuracy of my tricks.
My goal is to win the Red Bull Street Style World Finals in Italy and excite the audience while doing it!
